HEADWORD: Reeky
<hw>Reek"y</hw> <pr>(-?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[From 2d
<er>Reek</er>; cf. <er>Reechy</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Soiled with
